Here is a list of things that could be added to the electronics packaging lab. Pretty much all of it is replacement for very old items that we already have, but are extremely past the expiration date . Most of the items fit with the theme of a general packaging lab.  Some are things that synergize with other capabilities related to electronics and packaging (eg. stuff to make electronic inks for inkjet printing of electronic components). All of these items would be kept in that room.

 

